Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.25,0:00:08.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我愛妳 愛到出神陶醉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.29,0:00:16.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我愛妳 愛到懊惱萬分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.13,0:00:25.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我什麼也不怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.50,0:00:32.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我愛妳 無法忘記妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.84,0:00:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,風兒硬是拆開\N我們纏綿甜蜜的吻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.85,0:00:46.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,面對無法停止的熾熱心動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:46.12,0:00:49.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請不要流淚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.03,0:00:54.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,令人無法討厭的冷漠態度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:54.43,0:00:58.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,見不到面令我痛苦萬分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.14,0:01:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳鬱悶不樂的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:02.34,0:01:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,令我心碎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.08,0:01:08.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我愛妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.25,0:01:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我愛妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.36,0:01:25.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我愛妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.86,0:01:54.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳還真是性急啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.96,0:01:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不一點點慢慢整理的話\N年終的大掃除會很累的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.83,0:02:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每天都在清掃整理\N居然還有需要掃除的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.23,0:02:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真的無法想像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.57,0:02:08.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員,還有東西要燒的嗎?\N火快熄了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.04,0:02:11.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼,這是最後的了,很重喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.88,0:02:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽,地瓜好像快烤好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.05,0:02:16.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.96,0:03:37.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,#39 戀愛以膽量決勝負!\N五代打工大作戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.61,0:03:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼貴重的石頭嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.61,0:03:56.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就你能了解的範圍就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.95,0:03:58.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道這是什麼石頭嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.82,0:04:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然我自己也會去查\N也希望你幫忙查一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.36,0:04:08.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你會覺得很麻煩嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.19,0:04:10.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會,我怎麼會覺得麻煩呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.30,0:04:13.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.76,0:04:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算我去查了\N也不一定會知道…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.63,0:04:20.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的…不管結果怎樣都好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.77,0:04:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果只是一塊普通石頭\N也無所謂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.31,0:04:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一個人做沒把握
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.75,0:04:32.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且,這種事只能拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.38,0:04:36.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道可不可以?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.36,0:04:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.02,0:04:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以拜託你嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.69,0:04:45.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會盡力試試看的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.60,0:04:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,借看一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.21,0:05:08.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,古生代,有奧陶紀的味道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.39,0:05:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你吃得出來嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.99,0:05:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼吃得出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.59,0:05:16.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是隨便說說而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.11,0:05:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.12,0:05:40.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.15,0:05:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一直在這裡嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.92,0:05:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在漫畫區等你耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.66,0:05:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在看什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.29,0:05:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼,找個資料而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.07,0:05:59.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聖誕節就快到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.04,0:06:01.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.91,0:06:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,你沒錢嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.84,0:06:10.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不然你怎麼約我在書店見面呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.88,0:06:14.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是沒有錢啦\N只是剛好想查點資料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.42,0:06:15.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.70,0:06:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.54,0:06:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好貴喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.34,0:06:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這明明只是個石頭而已…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.44,0:06:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,石頭?不是啦\N我想要的是那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.05,0:06:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那隻貓咪的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.35,0:06:55.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是要你買來\N當作聖誕禮物送給我喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.00,0:07:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,你當然會參加吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.84,0:07:14.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代參不參加\N應該要看管理員吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.54,0:07:16.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.25,0:07:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的,居然馬上就承認了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.45,0:07:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員決定要參加
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.39,0:07:24.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,順便告訴你,三鷹也會來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.82,0:07:29.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,時序又到了聖誕節
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.19,0:07:31.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大街小巷響起聖誕節歌頌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.76,0:07:34.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,氣氛也逐漸被炒熱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.23,0:07:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,茶茶丸吹起一陣羅曼史風暴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.97,0:07:42.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,這是絕對不能錯過的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.54,0:07:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也來參加吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.81,0:07:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,就這麼敲定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.11,0:07:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.48,0:07:49.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.85,0:07:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請問費用是多少…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.59,0:08:06.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聖誕派對的費用\N送管理員的禮物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.96,0:08:08.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有小津江的禮物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.20,0:08:10.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這些是怎麼都省不掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.44,0:08:19.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼算,錢都不夠啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.62,0:08:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別傻了,如果有這麼好的打工\N我早就去做了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.99,0:08:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦!阪本,你也會打工啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.50,0:08:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為從聖誕節\N到過年這段期間最花錢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.24,0:08:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是說啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.04,0:08:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經跟我女朋友約好\N要去賽班島玩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.34,0:08:52.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,賽班島?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.41,0:08:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來只有這個辦法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.84,0:08:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想短期間賺到錢\N只好多兼幾個工作吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.02,0:09:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,你怎麼了?\N肚子痛嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.25,0:09:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我討厭你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.55,0:09:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.69,0:09:07.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我最討厭你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.11,0:09:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這一個禮拜是關鍵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.08,0:09:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,銀河戰士,大爆發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.71,0:10:02.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們在演什麼蠢戲啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.75,0:10:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要送人的是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.79,0:10:45.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.19,0:10:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思,請分開包裝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.23,0:10:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不要附卡片?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.90,0:10:53.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.16,0:10:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,緞帶要用什麼顏色?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.23,0:10:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胸針用綠色的,手環用紅色的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.04,0:11:09.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓您久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.55,0:11:11.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小姐,這個也麻煩包起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.53,0:11:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,省點錢好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.24,0:11:34.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.71,0:11:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請等一下,我馬上就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.51,0:11:45.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,查得出來嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.72,0:11:50.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阪本有個學長\N在做地質調查的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.59,0:11:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿給那個人看的話\N說不定會知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.39,0:11:56.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過,請不要太過期待喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.76,0:11:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萬一查不出來就傷腦筋了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.46,0:12:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.03,0:12:04.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼樣\N在舉行派對之前會有答案的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.40,0:12:07.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望能查得出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.28,0:12:24.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.45,0:12:27.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起來玩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.42,0:12:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇,管理員穿著丁字褲的姿態
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.86,0:12:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來他不是裝睡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.43,0:12:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代最近\N好像很拼命打工的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.07,0:12:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,照這麼看來\N今天是沒辦法舉行宴會了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.68,0:12:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法,今天就忍耐一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.58,0:12:49.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真無聊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.85,0:12:51.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,實在太無趣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.82,0:12:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了愛情,粉身碎骨地工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.76,0:13:01.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,睡得像海參一樣的你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.06,0:13:03.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真可愛啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.63,0:13:06.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真可愛喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.03,0:13:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真可愛吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.37,0:13:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正都是字數過多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.39,0:13:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我出門了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.96,0:13:41.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.40,0:13:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.43,0:13:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你今天會去音無家嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.67,0:13:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會的\N因為這是今年最後一次的家教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.07,0:13:52.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚一點我也會去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.81,0:13:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我們會在那裡碰面囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.95,0:13:59.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊\N對了,石頭的事就拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.95,0:14:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨天我覺得好興奮喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.52,0:14:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的希望能夠查出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.16,0:14:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思,把你叫住了\N你在趕時間,不是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.76,0:14:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係,啊…對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.67,0:14:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨,五代\N你要去跟小津江約會嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.37,0:14:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又來了,我是跟阪本有約啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.64,0:14:27.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我懂了,接著才要約會啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.14,0:14:28.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大嬸!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.78,0:14:33.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼晚點見,我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.05,0:14:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,逃走了,逃走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.95,0:14:39.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,茶茶丸,七點鐘\N不要遲到喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.68,0:15:03.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看起來不像是什麼寶石
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.41,0:15:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該只是普通的石頭吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.02,0:15:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些像米粒一點一點的東西\N感覺應該不太平凡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.39,0:15:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.49,0:15:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.32,0:15:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.96,0:15:19.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這一定是用來磨米的石頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.83,0:15:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,豬頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.90,0:15:24.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之,我會拿去給他看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.00,0:15:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天能問得出來嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.60,0:15:31.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛\N傍晚六點半在這裡見面吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.07,0:15:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,六點半…嗯,應該來得及
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.68,0:15:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼,由你買單囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.51,0:15:41.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阪本,你可別把這石頭弄丟了\N或者弄壞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.85,0:15:43.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有不可以吃掉喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.65,0:15:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰會吃啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.46,0:15:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,時序是聖誕夜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.23,0:15:54.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在滿天星空出現一顆流星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.70,0:15:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被這顆流星引導的\N東方三博士…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.74,0:16:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小津江
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.54,0:16:04.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聖誕快樂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.78,0:16:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聖誕快樂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.45,0:16:20.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(毛衣兌換券)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.06,0:16:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很努力想織一件毛衣\N可是來不及織完
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.79,0:16:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起,請稍微再等一下喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.54,0:16:35.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.71,0:16:36.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳喜歡嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.04,0:16:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很喜歡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.33,0:17:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼,我先走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.87,0:17:09.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,教練,你也會來參加\N今晚的派對吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.84,0:17:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思,我已經有約了\N謝謝惠顧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.71,0:17:14.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尾牙的時候我會出席的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.18,0:17:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難得的聖誕夜要跟誰約會啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.95,0:17:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天不是應該輪到裕子嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.95,0:17:20.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才不是呢,是多美子吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.55,0:17:22.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不對吧,是英代啦\N一共是3850圓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.62,0:17:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們不要胡說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.52,0:17:26.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底是誰?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.09,0:17:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們不認識的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.69,0:17:29.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇,是真命天女耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.39,0:17:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.86,0:17:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過,她本人似乎不這麼認為\N找您150圓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.70,0:17:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.10,0:17:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.94,0:17:50.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三鷹做事真是完美啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.28,0:17:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然稍微直接了一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.98,0:17:53.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一點都不在乎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.66,0:18:02.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快樂的羊兒是聖誕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.76,0:18:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼這麼早就來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.63,0:18:07.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天提早下班趕來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.70,0:18:10.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真的有在工作嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.50,0:18:12.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是祕密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.87,0:18:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朱美,來,工作囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.21,0:18:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幫我把這個掛在門口,好嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.61,0:18:25.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(今日已被包下,店主)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.35,0:18:30.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨,朱美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.69,0:18:32.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,你們兩個來得好早喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.92,0:18:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,過了中午就迫不急待想來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.13,0:18:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以想說就乾脆到茶茶丸來等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.43,0:18:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.54,0:18:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道會不會下雪?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.63,0:19:12.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳要找的東西找到了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.56,0:19:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找不到刊有照片的書
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.74,0:19:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是不可思議
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.71,0:19:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幾乎都已經忘了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.57,0:19:28.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一旦再度想起\N就好像著了魔似的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.94,0:19:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說不定不要想起來比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.89,0:19:38.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,忘了對妳比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.12,0:19:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…這種事我辦不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.17,0:19:55.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,今天到此為止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.84,0:19:57.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.34,0:20:01.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,郁子,給妳一個獎賞吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.55,0:20:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且聖誕節也到了,給妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.65,0:20:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼呢?可以打開來看嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.39,0:20:11.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.46,0:20:15.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你,我要掛在包包上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.66,0:20:18.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在想說\N該送妳什麼禮物才好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.37,0:20:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你說喔\N我想起一件很奇怪的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.40,0:20:30.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是叔叔送給嬸嬸的禮物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.67,0:20:33.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,惣一郎?\N對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.41,0:20:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他送了一顆這麼大的石頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.31,0:20:38.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上面還有一粒一粒奇怪的花樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.48,0:20:46.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這好像是叔叔\N送給嬸嬸唯一的禮物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.99,0:20:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算他是地質學的老師\N拿石頭當禮物也太奇怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.16,0:21:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請問…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.39,0:21:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.49,0:21:24.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那…那塊石頭…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.89,0:21:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.76,0:21:29.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有,算了,沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.45,0:21:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音無小姐?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.45,0:21:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.99,0:21:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳今天出門啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.72,0:21:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊,你今天怎麼沒有開車…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.86,0:21:59.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,因為今天要喝酒喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.83,0:22:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳接著要去茶茶丸吧\N我們一起去…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.20,0:22:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,你怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.94,0:22:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要去拿那塊石頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.61,0:22:11.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請你們先去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:58.82,0:23:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又錯失了送禮物給她的機會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.42,0:23:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,下雪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:04.16,0:23:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下雪了,下雪了,下雪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:09.47,0:23:11.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽,妳看,下雪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.90,0:23:15.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,對不起\N沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:15.30,0:23:18.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可以亂踢呢\N快向大哥哥道歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:23.25,0:23:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣會更有聖誕節的氣氛喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.38,0:23:26.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.04,0:23:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為出了一點差錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.31,0:23:54.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我晚一點才會到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.71,0:23:56.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過,我一定會去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.75,0:23:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請幫我轉告給管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:59.21,0:23:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相聚一刻下一回
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:59.85,0:24:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「令人心酸的溫柔\N聖誕節是戀愛的預兆!」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:03.92,0:24:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我討厭過聖誕節
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:16.13,0:24:18.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當我們互相凝視時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:18.63,0:24:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就會有一道奇妙的旋律\N在心中迴響著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:33.62,0:24:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無法用言語來表達愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:40.36,0:24:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只好彈奏起了鋼琴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:46.86,0:24:50.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請把夢丟進來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:50.17,0:24:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為我測量一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:53.97,0:24:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愛有多深
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:58.71,0:25:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用輕觸的嘴唇演奏著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:05.01,0:25:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,平靜的合聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:11.99,0:25:17.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使擁抱著妳依然惆悵滿懷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:18.03,0:25:23.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夢見了Fantasy
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:25.17,0:25:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開啟了只有我們兩人\N才看得見的門扉Fantasy
